    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "This is the one you\u2019ve been waiting for! We are thrilled to offer this absolute gem in mint condition\u2014it truly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. From the flawless exterior to the pristine interior, every detail has been meticulously maintained, making this a rare find for any serious buyer seeking perfection!",
