    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches or chips, and the interior remains in pristine condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, offering a like-new driving experience with all systems functioning exactly as intended. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle that is essentially indistinguishable from a brand-new model.",
