    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently has significant mechanical issues, including a failing transmission and an engine that requires a complete overhaul. The exterior is marred by heavy rust, deep dents, and failing paint, while the interior shows severe wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This car is best suited as a parts donor or a very intensive restoration project for someone with the necessary tools and expertise.",
      "price": 4800.0,
